eddy.lang.analysis

Class ExtensionCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • eddy.lang.analysis.ExtensionCalculator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompilationProperties, CompilerConstants

    public class ExtensionCalculator
extends java.lang.Object
implements CompilerConstants, CompilationProperties
    Computes the Extension from a Policy. The extension consists of all itemized Action interpretations. An action is a valid itemization of a Rule if the Action + Rule.Modality is subsumed by the Rule. The extension is used by the ConflictAnalyzer to detect Conflict, and by the LimitationPrinciple to compute the set of limiting rights.
    Author:
    Travis Breaux
